author: Divya Rao
title: Photos: Deepika Padukone Looks Every Bit The Diva She Is At Shahid Kapoor’s Birthday Bash
text:
Divya Rao Feb . 20 . 2017 
Shahid Kapoor , who is turning a year older in a week, threw an early birthday bash for his closest friends from B-Town last night, and everyone attended looking their fabulous best ! His Padmavati co-star Deepika Padukone also came along, and she looked like a million bucks! When does this woman not look amazing? How does she do this? Deepika Padukone
